data.meta_description:
vpam_arts on July 10, 2023: "VPAM Foundation is proud to announce a special performance by the sensational Gonzalez-Flores Family Trio, featuring members of the Grammy Award winning band Quetzal  @quetzalmusic during A Summer Soiree: The Illuminators Gala dinner program on Sat, July 29 6:00 p.m-8:30 p.m. for an unforgettable evening of art, music, fine food, dancing, friends and YOU! Learn more and purchase tickets at VPAM.org. 

The Gonzalez Family Trio is an invitation as to what you might hear on any given night in the Gonzalez-Flores home. Whether it's a jam, or an arranged composition, Quetzal Flores, Martha Gonzalez @marthartivista and Sandino Gonzalez-Flores explore and play together as a family often as a form of affection. They play to connect with each other, remind themselves of the great many things life has to offer, regardless of the restless world around them.
